info.author: Mauricio Wolff
info.description:
Verify and returns True if a given string is a valid Roman Numeral, if it's a
string.

Converts a Roman Numeral to Integer, if it's valid.
Converts a Integer to Roman Numeral, if it's lower or equal to 3888.

requires re
